Serialization>>
converts object into byte stream>>platform independent
to make object serializable>>java.io.Serializable interface
FileOutputStream>>makes new file
ObjectOutputStream>>converts object into byte stream>writeObject()method

Advantages of Serialization 

To save/persist state of an object. 
To travel an object across a network.

Deserialization>>
converts byte stream into objects back.
FileInputStream>>reads the file
InputObjectStream>>converts byte stream to object


